      "blockId": "1416fee1-c680-4b47-a9ce-ef04fec0db0d",
      "html": "Started going all digital again.<div>2000's tech.</div><div><br></div><div>Wrote an iTunes clone (iPod Manager) for Linux using Claude.</div><div>Fully functional.</div>",
